# Ministère de la Culture

Ministère de la Culture is French for Ministry of Culture.
It may refer to: (as a native name)
* Ministry of Culture (France);
* Ministry of Culture (Ontario), Canada;
* Ministry of Culture and Communications (Quebec), Canada;
* Ministry of Culture, Tourism and Handicrafts (Guinea);
* Ministry of Culture (Lebanon);
See also
* Minister of Culture
* Ministère de la Culture et de la Communication
